sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User
  participant UI as Web App
  participant Auth as Auth API
  participant Mail as Email Service

  User->>UI: Request password reset
  UI->>Auth: POST /forgot-password
  Auth->>Auth: Generate reset token
  Auth->>Mail: Send reset link
  Mail-->>User: Reset email delivered
  User->>UI: Open reset link and submit new password
  UI->>Auth: POST /reset-password
  Auth-->>UI: Password updated
  UI-->>User: Show success message
